*Ode* češljem po kosi. (He ran his comb through his hair.)

*Odela* se u novu haljinu za veče. (She dressed up in a new dress for the evening.)

*Odel* je u odoru džentlmena. (He put on a gentleman's attire.)

*Oda* se počast ocu uz čašu vina. (She paid tribute to her father with a glass of wine.)

*Odela* se u narodnu nošnju. (She put on traditional clothing.)

*Ode* u šetnju sa prijateljima. (He went for a walk with friends.)